</style>，是衡量模型复杂性的不变量 - 模型的粗粒度特征，可用于与其他模型进行高级比较。虽然具有相同的学习系数并不意味着两个模型是相同的，但具有不同的学习系数告诉我们两个模型<i>有质的</i>不同。</p><p>学习系数的独特之处在于它是<i>理论的</i>输出而不是临时的发明。除了损失本身之外，学习系数是比较不同模型的<i>最原则的</i>方式。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:62.61%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/fpkr8br7exid3xa7umwk" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/dclnfi4g46j6youm1v9d 110w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/zu1mgpzt9mnf1xwodnaa 220w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/pxiji45ik0ashiaoted7 330w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/bfbdufet028gfomsw8ea 440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/uw35st6vyyfqpjg5vlq1 550w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/jsmlhpxaafoaje50gon7 660w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/osdiajqlcrzsxan9etuo 770w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/cjljghg9w3sdphqqxheu 880w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/h1fevvcldfjwoeifefz6 990w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/bnbqvbqud9bunuzqppic 1028w"><figcaption> <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2308.12108">Lau 等人的图 5。 (2023)</a>证明了两种不同的优化器（SGD 和 entropy-SGD）在 MNIST 上找到了性质不同的解决方案，而 entropy-SGD 找到了更简单的解决方案。</figcaption></figure><h2>模型开发</h2><p><strong>模型比较对于研究模型开发是必要的。</strong> <a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/TjaeCWvLZtEDAS5Ex/towards-developmental-interpretability">我们有兴趣比较不同时期的模型，以了解它们是如何发展的</a>。像局部学习系数这样的高级可观察量使我们能够深入了解这个过程，而无需详细了解模型的内部机制。</p><p>特别是，我们的目标是了解学习过程中的相变——模型经历突然的、意想不到的转变的时刻。我们希望能够检测到这些转变，因为我们认为大部分风险包含在训练期间发生的价值观或能力的突然的、不希望的变化（〜急左转）以及上下文中发生的行为的突然的、不希望的变化（危险的转弯/机械异常）。</p><p>局部学习系数估计是构建用于检测和理解这些转变的工具的第一步。</p><p><strong>相变真的会出现吗？</strong>到目前为止，理论上预测的相变最容易确认的地方是<a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/1312.6120.pdf">深度线性网络</a>和<a href="https://transformer-circuits.pub/2022/toy_model/index.html">叠加玩具模型</a>等简化设置。对于较大的模型，我们预计相变是常见的但“隐藏的”。我们的 <a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/TjaeCWvLZtEDAS5Ex/towards-developmental-interpretability">当务之急</a>是测试这些转换的常见程度以及我们是否可以检测到隐藏的转换。</p><p><strong>深度线性网络。</strong>让我们考虑深度线性网络 (DLN) 的示例。这些是没有非线性激活的神经网络。就表现力而言，这些模型与简单的仿射变换相同，但就动力学而言，它们更有趣。观察到的<a href="https://browse.arxiv.org/pdf/2106.15933.pdf">“从鞍到鞍”的转变</a>涉及损失的突然跳跃，这与学习系数的突然增加相一致。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:60.53%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/iifllhshoi6wgobrly8a" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/nem1ocytx8zh2rt84jkj 132w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/ezqbdramtwmdqel47ska 212w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/edommwy10izruy4q7kx0 292w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/i2jdtlcfw7gvdsggpe11 372w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/dfgqvg4wvo9fntji5mr1 452w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/tmrfu0x2cmlb0i3westq 532w"><figcaption> <a href="https://github.com/timaeus-research/devinterp/blob/main/examples/dlns.ipynb">DLN</a>显示模型复杂性突然增加<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\hat\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-munderover"><span class="mjx-stack"><span class="mjx-over" style="height: 0.213em; padding-bottom: 0.06em; padding-left: 0.041em;"><span class="mjx-mo" style="vertical-align: top;"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">^</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-op"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> （<strong>橙色</strong>），同时损失突然减少（<strong>蓝色</strong>）。</figcaption></figure><h1>从盆地到模型复杂性</h1><p>在本节中，我们将通过尝试形式化盆地体积的工作定义来激发学习系数（通过它我们将看到我们真正关心的是盆地体积<i>缩放</i>）。我们将了解学习系数在何种意义上衡量模型复杂性，并检查相变的结果。</p><h2>棘手：盆地体积</h2><p><strong>盆体积和模型简单。</strong>学习理论家长期以来一直对盆地体积和模型简单性之间的联系感兴趣。我们并不真正关心我们最终会得到什么模型，只要它的损失低于某个阈值<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\epsilon"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。当阈值接近最小值时尤其如此：我们想知道在获得的解<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="w^*"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mo" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">*</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的邻域中有多少个“几乎一样好的”解。</p><p>直观上，更宽的盆地（具有更合适的模型）更简单。因为它们占用更多的体积，所以需要更少的位来定位。根据奥卡姆剃刀原理，我们需要最简单的解决方案来解决当前的问题<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=""><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"></span></span></span></span></span> 。 <span class="footnote-reference" role="doc-noteref" id="fnref1s1fnajc57s"><sup><a href="#fn1s1fnajc57s">[1]</a></sup></span></p><p><strong>测量盆地。</strong>特别是，给定损失<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="L(w) \le \epsilon"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">≤</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span>的</span></span></span></span></span>上限，我们想要计算以下体积（在两个参数的情况下为“面积”）：</p> <span><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="V(\epsilon) = \int_{L(w)\le\epsilon}\varphi(w) \mathrm{d}w"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.186em;">V</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.388em;"><span class="mjx-mo" style="vertical-align: 0.001em; padding-right: 0.388em;"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size2-R" style="padding-top: 1.109em; padding-bottom: 1.109em;">∫</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -1.303em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">≤</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">φ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">d</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>对于一些先前的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\varphi(w)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">φ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>超过权重<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="w"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。出于我们的目的，我们可以安全地忽略先验并将其视为常数。考虑下面的玩具损失情况，其中<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="V(\epsilon)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.186em;">V</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>由灰色投影表示。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/tssf1eqxtnlzflr6nm8i" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/baa1skcldj02s0qkkqk1 180w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/f4mlwkk4wrmq04rod0kp 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/vor3ytezkzzdpyydwoe2 540w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/ibqktl2miexwnm5qhcuz 720w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/zngyuvzaivae1uzbxq43 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/vhhllhzdh8zt6i7iik5m 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/woeev29jbbvsbivcfnbo 1260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/xoli20shvq3jfr3ykula 1440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/qzypegmefpvocukq4uun 1620w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/hcdwscvkunlee7glvnur 1777w"><figcaption>损失景观的卡通描绘（由随机抛物面之和建模）。<br>这<i>并不能</i>很好地代表现实世界的损失情况。</figcaption></figure><p><strong>模型复杂性和比较。</strong>给定盆地中的每个模型都具有相同的盆地体积。该度量是一个粗粒度的可观察量（很像热力学中的体积），它将权重空间划分为类似模型的子类。因此，看到两个模型具有相似的体积就增加了它们在计算上相似的可能性。相反，具有不同的体积/复杂性表明两个模型在质量上是不同的。</p><p>不幸的是，实际上计算盆地体积是很困难的。这是因为维度灾难（体积随维度呈指数级增长），并且因为我们只能通过在有限数据集<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="D_n=\{x_i\}_{i=1}^n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">D</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>上评估的经验损失<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="L(w)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span> n <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>来近似“真实”人口<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="L_n(w)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">损失</span></span></span><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="D_n=\{x_i\}_{i=1}^n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">{</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">}</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-stack" style="vertical-align: -0.315em;"><span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; padding-bottom: 0.255em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/hlhofkxeinkmjutsqzek" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/eutlrj7zqvmowgqr4uk1 154w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/btffzuozhovfquwxkqgy 234w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/iwnniljh5djjibaxhpz6 314w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/yxg41sit2f2zkpw2kpfv 394w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/khsa9jjcbapvwblrlaz6 474w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/f34wuvhkbrgfa3te3g91 554w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/gwoggjchjqry3fb9cxrv 634w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/rjbtsvkkpgfzrv7krp7x 714w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/q6wdfwpsbps8wnz9yy7f 794w"><figcaption>如果两个模型属于不同体积的盆地，那么它们很可能是性质不同的模型。计算这个是很棘手的。</figcaption></figure><h2>错误：盆地平整度</h2><p><strong>从宽阔到平坦。</strong>解决这个棘手问题的通常方法是使用泰勒展开式：只要我们足够接近盆地底部，我们就可以用多项式局部逼近盆地。</p><p><a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/QPqztHpToij2nx7ET/hessian-and-basin-volume">大多数人停留在二阶近似上</a>，将盆地建模为抛物面，其曲率由 Hessian 矩阵给出最小值。然后计算所得的表面积就很简单了。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/p05tmmzpw2qbsdz2kfk3" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/pqecavhvfdfkkfrkgkdf 154w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/xg3d1c6371airgbcbprx 234w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/chdo5fz8m3ls4qmo4dht 314w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/bg2z8rvxytqinm3kjkgj 394w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/wc4fiymxinf7rfxkrjqx 474w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/ld5xvbcotuvawlgmiglx 554w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/gpmj5qbmzhukodp5d9tf 634w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/fjtiynchugp8pzakmal1 714w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/cygcsfiq0athb9ikm5tn 794w"><figcaption><strong>左：</strong>原始盆地以及“真实”体积。<strong>右</strong>：使用以盆地最小值为中心的抛物面进行体积近似，其曲率由 Hessian 给出。<br>这是一个无效的近似值。</figcaption></figure><p><strong>不幸的是，这种近似是错误的</strong>。最小平坦度是盆地体积的一个糟糕的指标。根本问题是<a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/fovfuFdpuEwQzJu2w/neural-networks-generalize-because-of-this-one-weird-trick">神经网络是<i>奇异的</i></a>：它们的损失情况具有退化的临界点。在实践中，损失的 Hessian 矩阵通常有许多零特征值（<a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1611.07476">通常是大多数</a>）。当我们尝试用曲率为零的抛物面来近似体积时，我们天真地预测了非物理的无限体积。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/dj62o24stvt33awr8u7x" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/gffaeppastcqgewdcqy2 154w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/bh5t0xy7hrexmosel6lm 234w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/oreuegszqjbbe8hz1dec 314w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/vt8bsqvehqjv2ig82aqj 394w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/hghlyzsyhk6tv66ftqnz 474w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/cvsmdrgzhe8zpnvwlqlg 554w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/ydn95wnr2xgggoirzxfn 634w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/scf6io1iycp3bzvyaol7 714w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/ilt1ibulkchy0u5rwgjz 794w"><figcaption>当模型是奇异的时，损失景观在质量上与其二阶泰勒近似不同。这使得基于 Hessian 的卷无效。</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/QPqztHpToij2nx7ET/hessian-and-basin-volume?commentId=SbbDWXgQS8XBoJN2C">标准校正是向这些零特征值添加一个小常数</a>，从而稳定 Hessian 矩阵。我们得到一个非常大的体积，而不是无限的体积。但这没有抓住要点：当二阶项消失时，函数与其二阶泰勒近似之间的定性等价性就会消失，并且这些基于 Hessian 的近似变得无效。</p><p>相反，我们需要使用泰勒展开式中的高阶项。对体积的最低阶贡献将由展开中的最高阶项主导。</p><p><strong>平坦度≠宽度。</strong>在文献中，平坦度（在黑森矩阵的一个小决定因素的意义上）和宽广度经常被混为一谈。不幸的是：两者并不相同。盆地宽度是一个有趣的问题。最小平面度是一个错误的问题。</p><h2>相反：盆地尺寸</h2><p><strong>体积动态。</strong>我们关心的是相对数量，而不是绝对数量。但更重要的是，我们对<i>动态感兴趣：</i>随着学习的进展，音量如何变化。随着我们收集越来越多的数据，我们能够变得更具辨别力，并且我们的阈值<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\epsilon"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>会下降。那么，真正的问题是：体积如何随着<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\epsilon"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ 的</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>变化而变化？<i>即使在非退化的常规情况下，这也更相关。</i></p><p><strong>音量缩放 >; 音量。</strong>研究体积缩放解决了体积的其他几个问题。首先，对于足够小的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\epsilon"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，相对体积变得独立于<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\epsilon"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，这使我们能够消除对这种任意截止的依赖。此外，体积缩放在重新参数化下是不变的，并且即使在简并临界点附近也不会发散。</p><p><strong>学习系数作为有效维度。</strong>体积缩放为</p><span><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="V(\epsilon)\sim c\epsilon^\lambda\quad \text{as}\quad \epsilon \to 0."><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.186em;">V</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">∼</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">c</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.584em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 1em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">作为</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 1em; height: 0px;"></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ε</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">→</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>缩放指数<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>称为<strong>学习系数</strong>（或“ <a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/4eZtmwaqhAgdJQDEg/dslt-1-the-rlct-measures-the-effective-dimension-of-neural">真实对数规范阈值</a>”）。它起到有效维度的作用（最多为常数倍）。</p><p>让我们用一些例子来说明这一点。</p><p><strong>常规型号。</strong>首先，考虑<i> </i><i>常规</i>（=非奇异）模型的情况，其中损失景观没有退化临界点。在这种情况下，基于 Hessian 的近似成立，并且体积以指数<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda=d/2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">d</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">/</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>增长，其中<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="d"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">d</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>是维度数（或参数计数）。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/osog8ydbdkwogkug4le1" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/xduvdzuexmvhuf3rrmlj 160w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/nmbfoz30amvkjsbntcqi 320w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/d5vke1d4opnkh0pupbzm 480w, http