class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>中抽取样本，自然的想法是使用 MCMC 技术。解释为什么这些工作超出了本文的范围，并且在其他地方得到了很好的介绍，但这里重要的是标准 MCMC 方法遇到了维数灾难，这使得它们不适合更大的模型。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/b6ydymsdzxnrrri788ij" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/yrzc2vdmtssmtlzewslu 90w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/nn2zmy22ww0cbowojgja 180w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/ia7erahjwomtznk7qahc 270w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/t0iebiap68d3frzxa5w4 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/hmlawmbwjwx74cgocuaj 450w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/sdf2ulo6gs6oslfhn5io 540w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/jo1puzakqipah931nytm 630w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/qp43yvslxl5uizdkkvsa 720w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/pplzrww1ypjw3thzpasi 810w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/gcurf84fxitcjbmycey1 850w"><figcaption><strong>在玩具景观上比较 MCMC 和 SGD</strong> ， <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="L(w_1, w_2) = w_1^2w_2^4"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" 